	nge or cancelation at any time without notice. No refund will be owed if a
	n Opening Act is changed or canceled. Doors times subject to change Ticket
	s may not be resold or offered for resale. If we suspect tickets have been
	 purchased for resale purposes only\, we reserve the right to void or canc
	el the tickets without refund. Tickets obtained from unauthorized sources 
	may be invalid\, lost\, stolen or counterfeit and if so\, are void.\nPrice
